Tashiara smirks. <br>
Endaar makes a rude gesture at Tashiara. <br>
Lythe says, 'd00d!/!!'<br>
Kylarie says, 'wtf r u all usign emotes.... dum rolplayers'<br>
Tashiara says, 'u guys r 3 levls higher then me I only hav 221 hits'<br>
